net.antidot.api.common

Enum Status

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Status>
      • net.antidot.api.common.Status
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Status>

    public enum Status
extends java.lang.Enum<Status>
    Antidot search service status.

    Each Antidot search service is defined by a status. For production services, default status is @c stable.
